RELEASE
=======

-------------------------
Version 3.1.4  2013-07-20

 - Introduce Version.h and getVersionInfo()


-------------------------
Version 3.1.3  2013-07-15

 - Minor adjustment of configure.ac


-------------------------
Version 3.1.2  2013-07-06

 - update configure.ac, typo normal vector
 - change contents in ChangeLog and NEWS


-------------------------
Version 3.1.1  2013-07-03

 - update configure.ac to place header file with nobase_include_HEADERS


-------------------------
Version 3.1.0  2013-07-02

 - packaging by autotools


-------------------------
Version 3.0.1-beta  2013-06-09

 - Add function to record normal vector from a polygon at cut points
 - Update user's guide


-------------------------
Version 3.0.0-beta  2013-02-25

 - Eliminate compile option "-DIGNORE_NORMAL_DIRECTION" and "-DIGNORE_STL_NORMAL"
 - Add RepairPolygonData()
 - Introduce accessor class for grid information
 - Change interface and name of Cartesian version
 - Enable to assign minus values for 3D index of wrapper array class
 - OpenMP parallelization for Cartesian version
 - Change to calculate cut info with double precision
 - Update user's guide
 - Adjust to Polylib-2.2ï¼Œand TextParser-1.1


-------------------------
Version 2.0.5  2012-10-16

 - Correction of compilation procedure


-------------------------
Version 2.0.4  2012-09-06

 - Change compile procedure for FFVC


-------------------------
Version 2.0.3  2012-04-21

 - Compiler option "-DIGNORE_NORMAL_DIRECTION"
   calculate cut information assuming that the front-back sides of polygon is not unified.
 - Compiler option "-DIGNORE_STL_NORMAL"
   calculate normal without using normal vector in STL file.


-------------------------
Version 2.0.2  2011-05-12

 - Update user's guide
 - Adjust interface to Polylib2.0.2
 - Generate a reference of html version only from doxygen


-------------------------
Version 2.0.1  2011-05-09

 - Update user's guide
 - Read polygon group and its ID from Polylib parameter file


-------------------------
Version 2.0.0  2010-11-10

 - Correction of user's guide
 - Change API (eliminate arguments of Boundaries* bList)
 - Introduce an option to incorporate octree version or not
 - Change search order to -x, +x, -y, +y, -z, +z


-------------------------
Version 1.0.0  2010-04-28

 - Initial release
